# FastBrick ðŸš€

A simple CLI tool to generate FastAPI project structures.

## Installation

Install FastBrick using:
```sh
pip install fastbrick
```

## Run Server

Start the FastAPI server with:
```sh
uvicorn main:app --reload
```

